{
  "chapter": 32,
  "chapter_summary": "第三十二回\"知己仇敌\"讲述了李寻欢与郭嵩阳枫林决战的故事。李寻欢因心中牵挂林诗音而不愿赴约，但郭嵩阳非要与他一战。李寻欢主动认输，郭嵩阳却深受感动，认为能为他人而甘愿认输才是真正的英雄。两人惺惺相惜，郭嵩阳承诺若李寻欢战死必替他完成未了心愿。最终二人在枫林中展开决战，郭嵩阳铁剑势不可挡，折断了李寻欢的飞刀刀锋。但郭嵩阳主动认败，因为他看出李寻欢本有机会杀他却未出手。说书老人的孙女辫子姑娘旁观了这场对决，对二人的品格大加赞赏，并分析了李寻欢三次本可出手却未出手的时机。本章展现了\"对手即知己\"的主题——有资格做对手的人才有资格做知己。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_song_yang",
      "speaker_name": "郭嵩阳",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "就在这里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_guo_song_yang",
      "text": "今天……我不能和你交手！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_song_yang",
      "speaker_name": "郭嵩阳",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "你说什么？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_song_yang",
      "speaker_name": "郭嵩阳",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "你说你不能和我交手？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_song_yang",
      "speaker_name": "郭嵩阳",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_guo_song_yang",
      "text": "我承认败了！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_song_yang",
      "speaker_name": "郭嵩阳",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "李寻欢，李寻欢，你果然不愧为当世的英雄！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_guo_song_yang",
      "text": "英雄？像我这样的人能算是英雄？",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_song_yang",
      "speaker_name": "郭嵩阳",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "普天之下，也许只有你才能算得上是英雄！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_song_yang",
      "speaker_name": "郭嵩阳",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "你说你承认败了，是么……但我却知道一个人肯认输时需要多大的勇气，这句话我也许宁死也不愿说的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_song_yang",
      "speaker_name": "郭嵩阳",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "但死却容易多了，能为了别人而宁可自己认输，自己受委屈，这才是真正的英雄！真正的男子汉！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_guo_song_yang",
      "text": "你……",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_song_yang",
      "speaker_name": "郭嵩阳",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "我很了解你，你说你不能和我交手，只因你觉得你自己现在还不能死，你知道还有人需要你照顾，你不能抛下她不管！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_song_yang",
      "speaker_name": "郭嵩阳",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "但我今日还是非和你交手不可！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_guo_song_yang",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_song_yang",
      "speaker_name": "郭嵩阳",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "普天之下，又有几个李寻欢？今日我若不与你交手，他日再想找你这样的对手，只怕是永远找不到的了！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_guo_song_yang",
      "text": "只要此件事了了，阁下他日相邀，我随时奉陪。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_song_yang",
      "speaker_name": "郭嵩阳",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "到那时，你我只怕更无法交手了。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_guo_song_yang",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_song_yang",
      "speaker_name": "郭嵩阳",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "到那时，你我说不定已成了朋友！",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_guo_song_yang",
      "text": "宁可与我为敌，却不愿做我的朋友？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_song_yang",
      "speaker_name": "郭嵩阳",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "郭某此生已献与武道，哪有余力再交朋友？何况……",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_song_yang",
      "speaker_name": "郭嵩阳",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "朋友易得，能肝胆相照的对手却无处可寻……",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_song_yang",
      "speaker_name": "郭嵩阳",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "放眼天下，能与我一决生死的对手，自然不止你一人，但武力纵然强胜我十倍的人，我也未必放在眼里，若要我死在他们手上，更是心有不甘！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_guo_song_yang",
      "text": "不错，要找个能令你尊敬的朋友并不困难，要找个能令你尊敬的仇敌却太难了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_song_yang",
      "speaker_name": "郭嵩阳",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "正是如此，是以今日你我一战，势在必行，郭嵩阳今日纵然死于你手，亦是死而无憾！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_guo_song_yang",
      "text": "可是我……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_song_yang",
      "speaker_name": "郭嵩阳",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "你的意思我都了解，今日你若不幸战死，你的未了心愿，我必替你完成，你所要保护的人，我绝不容他人伤及她毫发。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_guo_song_yang",
      "text": "得此一言，李寻欢死有何憾？……多谢！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_song_yang",
      "speaker_name": "郭嵩阳",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "多谢成全，请！",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_guo_song_yang",
      "text": "请！",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_song_yang",
      "speaker_name": "郭嵩阳",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "我败了！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_guo_song_yang",
      "text": "谁说你败了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_song_yang",
      "speaker_name": "郭嵩阳",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "我承认败了！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_song_yang",
      "speaker_name": "郭嵩阳",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "这句话我本来以为死也不肯说的，现在说出了，心里反觉痛快得很，痛快得很，痛快得很……",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bian_zi_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "辫子姑娘",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "了不起，了不起，实在太了不起……",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bian_zi_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "辫子姑娘",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "能看到两位今日一战，连我也死而无憾的了！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bian_zi_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "辫子姑娘",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "昔日帝王谷主萧王孙与蓝大先生战于泰山绝顶，蓝大先生持百斤大铁锥，萧王孙用的却是根衣带，他以至柔敌至刚，与蓝大先生恶战一昼夜，据说天地皆为之变色，日月也失却光彩。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bian_zi_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "辫子姑娘",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "你说这一战精彩不精彩？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_bian_zi_gu_niang",
      "text": "听姑娘说得如此生动，我几乎也像是到了泰山绝顶，得见帝王谷主与蓝大先生的雄风，实在是精彩极了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bian_zi_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "辫子姑娘",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "想不到你说的话比你的飞刀还要厉害得多。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_bian_zi_gu_niang",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bian_zi_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "辫子姑娘",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "你一剑虽然可以要人的命，但你只要说一句话，却可令女孩子们将心都交给你，要女人的心，岂非比要男人的命困难多了么？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bian_zi_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "辫子姑娘",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "昔年'水母'阴姬号称天下第一高手，但'侠盗'楚留香的胆子却比天还大，竟直闯神水宫，独斗阴姬，两人由地上打到水里，再由水里打到半空，'水母'阴姬的武功虽无敌，到最后还是被楚留香打败了！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bian_zi_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "辫子姑娘",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "你说这一战精彩不精彩？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_bian_zi_gu_niang",
      "text": "精彩极了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bian_zi_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "辫子姑娘",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "这些战役虽然惊天动地，而且还能名留千古，但比起两位方才那一战来，却还是差得远了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_bian_zi_gu_niang",
      "text": "我一向不是个谦虚的人，却也有自知之明，姑娘也未免太过奖了吧。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bian_zi_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "辫子姑娘",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "我说的是真话，你本有三次机会可致郭嵩阳的死命，但却都未出手，到后来你杀气已竭，刀锋已折，郭嵩阳说不定已可将你置之于死地，但他却心甘情愿地认败服输了……",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bian_zi_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "辫子姑娘",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "像你们这样，才真正是男子汉大丈夫，才真正无愧于英雄本色，你若一刀杀了他，他若一刀杀了你，你们的武功就算再高，我也不会瞧在眼里。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 320
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_bian_zi_gu_niang",
      "text": "郭嵩阳的确不愧为真英雄！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bian_zi_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "辫子姑娘",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "你呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 324
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_bian_zi_gu_niang",
      "text": "我？……我又算得了什么！",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 326,
      "line_end": 326
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bian_zi_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "辫子姑娘",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "我问你，他第一剑挥出，用的是什么招式？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 330
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_bian_zi_gu_niang",
      "text": "风卷流云。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 332,
      "line_end": 332
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bian_zi_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "辫子姑娘",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "第二招呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 334
